        h2 Synchronise Applications
        p Utilise Joukou’s distributed database to synchronise data between multiple locations. Joukou can act as a central repository for data helping businesses to maintain data consistency across multiple sites. Joukou’s multi-site architecture ensures data redundancy and consistency, and will improve access to data.
