        h2 Monetise Assets
        p More than just a tool Joukou is also a network of users, businesses and developers. We provide a platform to facilitate the trading of data, Joukou connectors, and services built on the Joukou infrastructure.
        p Joukou is passionate about unifying and liberating data. We’re not just a means for connecting data, we’re a way to open and enable your business.
