        h2 Why use Joukou
        p Using Joukou saves your business money. With a simple and intuitive user interface people with minimal technical skills are empowered to repurpose data with little to no help from IT resources. This will improve delivery times for integration projects, reduce on-going IT maintenance costs, and free up IT resources for more pressing matters.
        p As a managed service Joukou allows your business to outsource your data infrastructure reducing short-term costs and technical debt. As your business's data requirements change the Joukou service can be scaled for your needs, all within a future-proof and secure environment. Joukou gives your business enterprise-quality data-repurposing tools at a fraction of the cost.
